category: Gnome
requires: python python-gobject2.0 python-gtk2.0 python-gconf2 python-gtksourceview2 python-gnome2
sdesc: "GNOME jotter application"
ldesc: "gjots2(1) is a simple jotter application for your desktop - an 
outline processor. You can use gjots2(1) to organise your jottings into 
a tree structure, adding thoughts and miscellany as you go. You can get 
it to spit out HTML, XML, postscript, pdf, man, etc."
